{"tha-ap391:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap391:0.2":"Avataphalavagga ","tha-ap391:0.3":"9 Sonakotivisattheraapadana ","tha-ap391:1.1":"“Vipassino pavacane, ","tha-ap391:1.2":"ekam lenam maya katam; ","tha-ap391:1.3":"Catuddisassa sanghassa, ","tha-ap391:1.4":"bandhumarajadhaniya. ","tha-ap391:2.1":"Dussehi bhumim lenassa, ","tha-ap391:2.2":"santharitva pariccajim; ","tha-ap391:2.3":"Udaggacitto sumano, ","tha-ap391:2.4":"akasim panidhim tada. ","tha-ap391:3.1":"Aradhayeyyam sambuddham, ","tha-ap391:3.2":"pabbajjanca labheyyaham; ","tha-ap391:3.3":"Anuttaranca nibbanam, ","tha-ap391:3.4":"phuseyyam santimuttamam. ","tha-ap391:4.1":"Teneva sukkamulena, ","tha-ap391:4.2":"kappe navuti samsarim; ","tha-ap391:4.3":"Devabhuto manusso ca, ","tha-ap391:4.4":"katapunno virocaham. ","tha-ap391:5.1":"Tato kammavasesena, ","tha-ap391:5.2":"idha pacchimake bhave; ","tha-ap391:5.3":"Campayam aggasetthissa, ","tha-ap391:5.4":"jatomhi ekaputtako. ","tha-ap391:6.1":"Jatamattassa me sutva, ","tha-ap391:6.2":"pitu chando ayam ahu; ","tha-ap391:6.3":"Dadamaham kumarassa, ","tha-ap391:6.4":"visakoti anunaka. ","tha-ap391:7.1":"Caturangula ca me loma, ","tha-ap391:7.2":"jata padatale ubho; ","tha-ap391:7.3":"Sukhuma mudusamphassa, ","tha-ap391:7.4":"tulapicusama subha. ","tha-ap391:8.1":"Atita navuti kappa, ","tha-ap391:8.2":"ayam eko ca uttari; ","tha-ap391:8.3":"Nabhijanami nikkhitte, ","tha-ap391:8.4":"pade bhumya asanthate. ","tha-ap391:9.1":"Aradhito me sambuddho, ","tha-ap391:9.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap391:9.3":"Arahattanca me pattam, ","tha-ap391:9.4":"sitibhutomhi nibbuto. ","tha-ap391:10.1":"Aggo araddhaviriyanam, ","tha-ap391:10.2":"niddittho sabbadassina; ","tha-ap391:10.3":"Khinasavomhi araha, ","tha-ap391:10.4":"chalabhinno mahiddhiko. ","tha-ap391:11.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap391:11.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap391:11.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap391:11.4":"lenadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap391:12.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap391:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap391:12.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap391:13.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap391:13.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap391:13.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap391:14.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap391:14.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap391:14.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap391:15.1":"Thero kotiviso sono, ","tha-ap391:15.2":"bhikkhusanghassa aggato; ","tha-ap391:15.3":"Panham puttho viyakasi, ","tha-ap391:15.4":"anotatte mahasareti. ","tha-ap391:16.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sono kotiviso thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap391:17.1":"Sonakotivisattherassapadanam navamam. "}